{"tid":2218492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疑拍片屈民主黨派錢 警受查","createTime":"2020-09-26T08:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T08:57:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"29783f6fde25bc227c6dc00c2fbea7de1f21c082","tid":2218492,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:57:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200926/WYPGZ776NNFILJH3YEW7MPPIHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2FWYPGZ776NNFILJH3YEW7MPPIHA%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=a147eb87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2FWYPGZ776NNFILJH3YEW7MPPIHA%2F&h=8261c5b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200926/WYPGZ776NNFILJH3YEW7MPPIHA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n疑拍片屈民主黨派錢 警受查<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_k8xPvpAa6FNK4KSi70aI2_GFhA=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CAXCU5Q4T5H35LPE4ILZMNLCQU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_k8xPvpAa6FNK4KSi70aI2_GFhA%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCAXCU5Q4T5H35LPE4ILZMNLCQU.jpg&h=2cccd9b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭麗琼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今年3月中西區區議會主席鄭麗琼被警方以涉「煽動意圖」拘捕，鄭的民主黨黨友在警署外就鄭的保釋金「夾錢」時疑被警員拍攝，其後建制陣營流傳短片，指民主黨向聲援鄭的人士派錢。該黨中西區區議員甘乃威表示，投訴警察課通知會立案調查拍片事件，並循涉嫌有警員行為失當方向調查，不過甘坦言對調查「沒有期望也不會失望」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當日為鄭麗琼保釋金夾錢<br />\n<br />\n鄭麗琼3月26日凌晨被捕，多名黨友到葵涌警署聲援鄭。鄭同日獲釋後，建制陣營流傳短片，指控民主黨成員向聲援鄭的人士派錢，民建聯副主席陳學鋒亦轉載該短片。當時民主黨許智峯已解釋他們並非派錢，而是一眾黨友為鄭麗琼的保釋金夾錢，該短片的拍攝角度屬警署範圍，民主黨質疑有警員與建制派合流。<br />\n<br />\n其後甘乃威向警察投訴課投訴，他昨收到投訴警察課通知已立案，循涉嫌有警員行為失當的方向調查，個案亦被界定為須向監警會滙報個案。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n甘稱，事發至今經已六個月，「要查都查晒啦」，再者警署內外均有閉路電視，亦有出入警署人士紀錄，加上他曾提交書面證供，相信投訴課有足夠資料調查。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NCYM4fQWx6dETidnP4ELASaVmAA=/808x348/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TN5DTKYU6RFJPHWUXEHSOFOD64.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNCYM4fQWx6dETidnP4ELASaVmAA%3D%2F808x348%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTN5DTKYU6RFJPHWUXEHSOFOD64.gif&h=dc4a745d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■今年3月民主黨黨員被拍得在葵涌警署外為鄭麗琼的保釋金夾錢（左圖），當時有男子在警署內舉機（右圖）。"}]}